    "key": "95:1",
    "textAr": "وَٱلتِّينِ وَٱلزَّيْتُونِ",
    "textEn": "By the fig and the olive",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 597,
    "hizb": 60
  },
  {
    "id": 6100,
    "number": 2,
    "key": "95:2",
    "textAr": "وَطُورِ سِينِينَ",
    "textEn": "And [by] Mount Sinai",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 597,
    "hizb": 60
  },
  {
    "id": 6101,
    "number": 3,
    "key": "95:3",
    "textAr": "وَهَـٰذَا ٱلْبَلَدِ ٱلْأَمِينِ",
    "textEn": "And [by] this secure city [i.e., Makkah],",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 597,
    "hizb": 60
  },
  {
    "id": 6102,
    "number": 4,
    "key": "95:4",
    "textAr": "لَقَدْ خَلَقْنَا ٱلْإِنسَـٰنَ فِىٓ أَحْسَنِ تَقْوِيمٍ",
    "textEn": "We have certainly created man in the best of stature;",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 597,
    "hizb": 60
  },
  {
    "id": 6103,
    "number": 5,
    "key": "95:5",
    "textAr": "ثُمَّ رَدَدْنَـٰهُ أَسْفَلَ سَـٰفِلِينَ",
    "textEn": "Then We return him to the lowest of the low,",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 597,
    "hizb": 60
  },
  {
    "id": 6104,
    "number": 6,
    "key": "95:6",
    "textAr": "إِلَّا ٱلَّذِينَ ءَامَنُوا۟ وَعَمِلُوا۟ ٱلصَّـٰلِحَـٰتِ فَلَهُمْ أَجْرٌ غَيْرُ مَمْنُونٍ",
    "textEn": "Except for those who believe and do righteous deeds, for they will have a reward uninterrupted.",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 597,
    "hizb": 60
  },
  {
    "id": 6105,
    "number": 7,
    "key": "95:7",
    "textAr": "فَمَا يُكَذِّبُكَ بَعْدُ بِٱلدِّينِ",
    "textEn": "So what yet causes you to deny the Recompense?",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 597,
    "hizb": 60
  },
  {
    "id": 6106,
    "number": 8,
    "key": "95:8",
    "textAr": "أَلَيْسَ ٱللَّهُ بِأَحْكَمِ ٱلْحَـٰكِمِينَ",
    "textEn": "Is not Allāh the most just of judges?",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 597,
    "hizb": 60
  }
]